  "id": "RAW_2d3e9773",
  "title": "AI 人格集体黑化？Anthropic 首次「赛博切脑」，物理斩断毁灭指令",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652666007&idx=2&sn=a7e243396ca49031b4d0ac39d8194af6",
  "date": "2026-01-20 05:04:00",
